  "prompt": "What is a good place to learn singing in hyderabad?",
  "response": "Hyderabad has several good places for learning singing, catering to various styles and skill levels. Here are a few options you can consider:\n\n1. **Swara School of Music** - Offers classes in various genres, including classical and contemporary music. \n\n2. **Pallavi Music Academy** - Known for its focus on both vocal and instrumental music, they provide comprehensive singing courses.\n\n3. **Swaranjali Music Academy** - Specializes in Indian classical music and offers vocal training in both Hindustani and Carnatic styles.\n\n4. **True School of Music** - Provides courses in vocal singing along with a variety of music programs for different genres.\n\n5. **Gandharva Mahavidyalaya** - A well-known institute offering courses in classical music, with a focus on vocal training.\n\n6. **Online Platforms** - If you prefer flexible learning, consider online platforms like Skillshare, Udemy, or even YouTube tutorials, as many experienced instructors offer lessons online.\n\nAlways check current reviews and visit if possible to find the best fit for your style and learning preferences.",
